Class Configuration

java.lang.Object
  com.netcracker.tc.model.Configuration

public class Configuration
extends Object

Test cases configuration, contains list of test configurations, sends events about configuration changes on all levels (test cases configuration, test case, test scenario, test scenario parameter).
